Ash and his friends have been on the road for quite a while now,
so they have decided to take a little break in a beautiful meadow.
Hey, what are you looking at, a new kind of Pokemon?
Uh, there was a rumor that one's been spotted right near here.
It looks like it is holding a leek in its wing.
Farfetch'd makes a delicious meal, especially when cooked with leek.
Because of this, Farfetch'd is nearly extinct.
Hey, if it is that valuable, I will capture it.
There is supposed to be a spring nearby and we need to get some water.
Ah, my legs are tired from walking.
Hey, I do not have the energy to deal with you.
If I have to look at that face, I am going to get a headache.
-Time for you to go back in your ball.
Wow, I do not believe it.
That is Farfetch'd, the rare Pokemon.
Ha, that is the coolest Pokemon ever.
While Ash and Brock are gone, I am going to capture it myself.
Come out, come out, wherever you are.
I am in no mood for a marathon, Farfetch'd.
-You will not get away from me! -
I was not looking where I was going.
Well, I was not paying attention either.
Oh, now I have lost track of Farfetch'd.
Oh, how could I let it get away?
Where did you run off to?
Oh, I found a Farfetch'd and tried to capture it but it got away.
Have you been sneaking around behind our backs?
If I caught it, it would have been all of ours.
Anyway, Farfetch'd is an incredible Pokemon.
Oh, it is so cute and it twirls it is leek like a baton.
I am telling the truth this time.
-I must have picked up the wrong backpack.
Just like taking candy from a baby, eh, Farfetch'd?
Now, let us see what is inside.
This must be all of her Pokemon.
That must have been when the backpacks were switched.
I had all the Pokemon I ever caught in that backpack!
Are you sure there are Farfetch'd out here in the middle of nowhere?
Trust me, we will find some.
I hear people are spotting Farfetch'd in this forest all the time.
We come to look for it and it comes to us.
It tastes good and has good taste.
And it looks so happy to see us.
Sounds like you guys like my Farfetch'd.
I was just planning on getting rid of my Farfetch'd anyway.
You guys want to make a deal with me?
I have a Starmie and a Staryu in here too.
I guess I am sort of getting tired of raising Pokemon.
I would be happy to find somebody who would take them off my hands.
I forgot something back in the forest.
Would you mind watching my Poke Balls and my Farfetch'd while I run and get it?
We will take care of them.
And I will be right back.
This is easier than taking candy from a baby.
Letting Team Rocket guard your Pokemon is like
letting your cat guard your canary.
I cannot believe how stupid he is.
And look, he even left a boat for us to make our getaway.
He is done all the work for us.
Too bad he did not leave his recipe for Farfetch'd flambe.
-And he left a Starmie and Staryu.
Heh, this was the simplest Pokemon capture in Team Rocket history.
Maybe that is the key to success.
Maybe we should just let good things happen to bad people.
-Quick, plug that hole before we sink.
We can use his Starmie and Staryu to bring them back.
I think he might have taken my backpack by accident.
-The Farfetch'd came and then did a trick.
-I am sorry but that was no accident.
You are the fifth victim of the backpack-switching thief this week.
You were tricked by that boy and his Farfetch'd.
Jenny, you have to help me.
That thief and Farfetch'd stole every Pokemon I had.
I have been trying to track him down for a while but never he stays in one place.
-He is a slippery one, that kid. -
We have been together for a long time, Farfetch'd.
Right after I found you injured on the road and nursed you back to health,
I wish there was some other way for us to get by,
but... how else are we ever going to survive?
-We are just too weak to battle.
Well, I think our stew is ready.
We are going to find that no-good, rotten crook and show him
what good rotten crooks are like.
And I cannot believe he tricked us so easily.
-It is because you were so stupid.
But Meowth was the one who fell for his trick in the first place.
Let us save all our nastiness for that lousy kid.
This is the place I ran into him.
Oh, I cannot believe he stole all my Pokemon.
-Oh, I wish I could forget Psyduck.
Ah, I am so happy to see you.
-But how did you get back here?
-Well, then how did you get away?
- Where is the guy who stole you?
-Ah, now you are giving me a headache!
Okay, Psyduck, tell us which way to go.
-Yeah, Misty, you have got to relax.
Psyduck's trying as hard as he can to remember where the others are.
-does not sound like a good idea.
Well, if we meet someone on the road, we will just have to take their Pokemon too.
You thought you were going to get away with it, did not you?
Sinking that boat and grabbing our Pokemon.
Now we are going to make you pay for making fools of us.
Hey, come on, cannot you guys take a joke?
I really am sick of raising Pokemon.
Look, I will give you Arbok and Weezing and Lickitung and we will call it even.
You cannot make it up by just giving them back.
So I will give you all of these and my apologies.
-Well, since he is being so generous.
I am glad I ran into you guys.
I was planning on moving anyway but I just had too much stuff to carry.
So please forgive me and good luck.
Well, it looks like the kid was not so bad after all.
You act like a quack most of the time but you are pretty smart, Psyduck.
-Well, I guess we better get going.
Give me back my Pokemon right now, you thief.
You are under arrest for grand theft Pokemon.
What makes you think it was okay to lie and cheat people
so you could steal their Pokemon?
It takes a lot of love and care to raise Pokemon.
We worked real hard to train them all to win their Pokemon battles.
by showing this kid just how difficult a Pokemon match is.
That is not true at all.
Pokemon will become stronger with trainers who work with them.
You mean you want to battle?
Let us start our Pokemon battle.
At least now you can see the right way to capture Pokemon in the wild.
I did not know Farfetch'd could do that.
I never thought Farfetch'd had attacks like that.
You really did not know about its powers?
If I had known it was this strong, I would not have used it to steal.
You cannot judge a Pokemon by the way it looks.
He robbed me, so it is my job to battle him.
I did not get my Poke Balls back yet.
-Hit. Hit. Hit. Hit. Hit. Hit. Hit. Hit... -Psy!
I am embarrassed for ever doubting that kid.
Let us open up these Poke Balls
and find out what kind of great Pokemon he gave us.
We will get him for this.
I will not do anything bad anymore!
I will give back all the Pokemon I stole.
None the victims are going to press charges
since they all got their Pokemon back.
-It is great to have my old backpack back.
It was wrong to steal and it was wrong not to believe in Farfetch'd.
Now I am going to train Farfetch'd to become even stronger.
That is the way it should be.
Now you see that Pokemon can be anything a good trainer wants it to be.
Misty might have lost her Pokemon for good,
but thanks to a little help from Psyduck.
Or rather, thanks to a lot of help from Psyduck.
and everyone learned an important lesson about honesty, bravery and trust.
Are you sure you want to tell the boss about this?
Team Rocket cannot allow anyone to steal Pokemon.
If we tell the boss how the kid outsmarted us,
he will want to make him part of Team Rocket.
-He will be in and we will be out.
Then we will just have to tell him...
Absolutely nothing about that kid or Farfetch'd.
That is what we will do.
Looks like Team Rocket's blasting off again!
